<h1>Nijaat Productions</h1>

<p>Ambedkarite Artists Creating Anti-Caste Cinema</p>

</header>


<section>

<h2>About</h2>

<p>
Nijaat Productions is a collective of Ambedkarite artists committed to building a casteless society as envisioned by Dr. Babasaheb Ambedkar. Through cinema, documentaries, and digital media, we challenge caste oppression and amplify marginalized voices.
</p>

<p>
We believe art is a weapon of resistance. Our films document anti-caste struggles, Dalit artists, activists, and social realities ignored by mainstream media. Social media allows us to bypass traditional gatekeeping and connect directly with people.
</p>

</section>


<section>

<h2>Films</h2>

<div class="film">

<h3>Gun Gondhal (2023)</h3>

<p>
Debut feature film exploring caste realities and social contradictions.
</p>

</div>


<div class="film">

<h3>Kadubai</h3>

<p>
